data.description: Welcome to 9301 Buckman Ave. Centrally located with easy access to the beach, bases, downtown and the rest of Hampton Roads. The house has been well maintained since its recent renovation. It features 3 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms, 2 inviting living spaces plus a stylish kitchen. This home is sits on a corner lot with a fenced front yard and a driveway parking pad on the side of the home.  Check this out today before it's gone!
